quote.summary: Zhongmiao Holdings Qingdao Co Ltd is a China-based company primarily engaged in the provision of insurance agency service and solutions. The Company conducts its business through three segments. The Insurance Agency Business segment is engaged in distributing four categories of insurance products including property insurance products, life and health insurance products, accident insurance products and automobile insurance products. The Information Technology (IT) services segment is engaged in the provision of digitalised solutions that cover the main processes of insurance business. The major software/systems include insurance marketing and sales system, insurance claims system, online training system, insurance intermediary core business system and artificial intelligence (AI) service system. The Consulting Services segment mainly includes human resources consulting services and marketing and promotion services. The Company mainly conducts business in the domestic market.
